Description: This dataset contains structured field survey responses collected from water point inspections and interviews with community members or water point committee representatives. Each record represents a single survey event linked to a specific water point, including GPS coordinates, enumerator metadata, timestamps, and detailed observations on infrastructure condition, functionality, water availability, maintenance practices, and governance arrangements.
